Currently, your logger is already filtering out `[Server] GET` debug messages through the `shouldLog` method. I'll enhance this to provide a more configurable filtering system that lets you selectively enable/disable different types of log messages.

## List of Updates to `logger.js`

- Add a filter configuration system to the logger
- Enhance `shouldLog` method to use the filter configuration
- Add methods to dynamically set/update filters
- Update constructor to accept filter configurations

```javascript
