4. Generates an HMAC-SHA256 signature using the secret key
5. Forms the Authorization header in the format Onshape expects: `On {accessKey}:HmacSHA256:{signature}`
6. Returns all necessary headers for the API request

This implementation follows the standard pattern for API key authentication with Onshape and should resolve the error you're experiencing.

